I think it's
a lack of self-confidence.

53
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,529
I mean, I know you go out
on dates and everything...

54
00:02:53,563 --> 00:02:55,463
but I think when you find
the girl of your dreams...

55
00:02:55,498 --> 00:02:57,159
you can't seal the deal,
you know?

56
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,963
Pick the fruit, spit the wad.

57
00:02:59,002 --> 00:03:02,438
-You know what I'm saying?
-No, I don't.

58
00:03:02,472 --> 00:03:04,463
BOY: I think what your friend
is trying to say...

59
00:03:04,507 --> 00:03:06,941
is that you're suffering
from a classic psychosomatic...

60
00:03:06,976 --> 00:03:09,069
communicative anxiety disorder.

61
