Hey, Nathan, how's it going?

79
00:00:04,712 --> 00:00:06,942
I got to spend another
one of my remaining days...

80
00:00:06,981 --> 00:00:08,346
in this purgatory.

81
00:00:08,383 --> 00:00:11,079
I got cataracts
the size of cantaloupes...

82
00:00:11,119 --> 00:00:13,087
